Package: crun
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Provides: oci-runtime
Description: Fast and lightweight fully featured OCI runtime
 crun is a fast and low-memory footprint OCI Container Runtime
 fully written in C. It supports all OCI runtime spec features
 and serves as the default runtime for Podman.
